screen_desc: The screenshot shows a ride-hailing app interface with the title "Plan your ride." The user can select "Pickup now" or choose a different time. There are fields to enter the pickup location and destination. Below these fields, there are options to search in a different city, set the location on a map, and access saved places. The keyboard at the bottom of the screen is visible, with a background image of a tent under a starry sky.
